de: Im Westen Sydneys könnten die 40-Grad-Marke knacken, wenn eine Hitzewelle über Australien rollt. Die erste Hitzewelle des Sommers wird heute in ganz New South Wales ihren Höhepunkt erreichen. Temperaturen über 40 Grad Celsius dürften sich vom Nordwesten Westaustraliens bis nach Parramatta erstrecken.
title: Sydney's west could crack 40 degrees as heatwave rolls across Australia
description: The first heatwave of the summer will reach its peak across New South Wales today, with temperatures above 40 degrees Celsius likely to span from Western Australia's north-west all the way to Parramatta.
en: Sydney's west could crack 40 degrees as heatwave rolls across Australia. The first heatwave of the summer will reach its peak across New South Wales today, with temperatures above 40 degrees Celsius likely to span from Western Australia's north-west all the way to Parramatta.
la: Sydney occidens 40 gradus resilire potuit sicut aestus aestus per Australiam volvitur. Prima aestus aestatis suum apicem trans Novam Australem Walliam hodie attinget, cum temperaturis supra 40 gradus Celsius usque ad occasum Australiae occidentis spatium usque ad Parramattam.
